OL,7,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar has
OL,8,Fpledged to do "whatever it takes" to
OL,9,Ftackle the "waiting times emergency"
OL,10,Fin the NHS.
OL,12,FWith hundreds of thousands of Scots
